  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/777020/extras/34e1d1434903b3a93eea24e14068572b.avif?t=1521456114\" width=550 height=150 /></span><br> «Mumps» — This is a fast, colorful and excellent 2D platformer with a pretty pink pig. The protagonist is a pink pig who called Mumps. Help the Mumps to avoid obstacles, pass all levels and get all the acorns. Feel like a pig and survive by collecting acorns. <br><br>● Unlock all Steam achievements. <br>● Pink platforms disappear when you touch it. <br>● Avoid Red Spikes.<br><br>Controls:<br>[Spacebar] or [Mouse click] - Jump<br>[R] - Restart game<br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > - Pause</p>",
